entries.content: Objections are not rejections but opportunities to provide information and address concerns.
entries.notes: Implied in the aggressive, no-excuses approach to sales.

entries.content: Taking ownership of sales struggles means viewing objections as part of the process, not external blame.
Professionalism in sales involves handling objections methodically, not personally.

focus_area: Objection Mindset: Objections = info requests, not rejections
